eptember 2011 (<small>season 1</small>)<br>15 April 2013 (<small>season 2</small>)<br>30 May 2015 (<small>season 3</small>)\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{BBC programme}}\n*[http://www.chilevision.cl/home/index.php?option=com_content&task=blogcategory&id=981&Itemid=1807 Chilean version]\n*[http://www.tvsa.co.za/showinfo.asp?showid=3541 South African version]\n*[http://www.tvp.pl/rozrywka/teleturnieje/dzieciaki-gora Polish version]\n*[http://ww1.rtp.pt/icmblogs/rtp/novidades/?Super-Miudos-com-Silvia-Alberto.rtp&post=21879 Portuguese version]\n*{{UKGameshow|The_Kids_Are_All_Right|The Kids Are All Right}}\n*{{IMDb title|1223172|The Kids Are All Right}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2012}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kids Are All Right}}\n[[Category:BBC television game shows]]\n[[Category:2000s British game shows]]\n[[Category:2000s British television series]]\n[[Category:2008 British television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2008 British television series endings]]\n[[Category:Television series by Endemol]]\n\n\n{{UK-tv-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Joeykai", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:clean up, removed stub tag", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Kids_Are_All_Right_(game_show)"}
